{"tid":1898668,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"派1萬蚊比18歲或以上香港永久性居民，有約700萬人受惠？","createTime":"2020-02-26T07:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T08:24:23.000Z","uid":53673,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"870f8273e6b29b0fa3d10c5d62311b5f2cbe5ab3","tid":1898668,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2020/chi/budget09.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2020%2Fchi%2Fbudget09.html&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X%2F4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=b1c07c0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.budget.gov.hk/2020/chi/budget09.html</a><br />\n<br />\n36. 經詳細考慮後，我會向<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">十八歲或以上的香港永久性居民</span></span>發放一萬元，一方面鼓勵及帶動本地消費，另一方面紓緩市民的經濟壓力。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">預計措施可惠及約七百萬人</span></span>，涉及約七百一十億元開支。政府會在立法會撥款後，盡快公布計劃的細節。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十八歲以上既香港永久性居民有700萬咁多？<br />\n睇下2016年既中期人口普查先：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bycensus2016.gov.hk/tc/bc-mt.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bycensus2016.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fbc-mt.html&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X%2F4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=a762dc7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bycensus2016.gov.hk/tc/bc-mt.html</a><br />\n[A103a<br />\n按性別、年齡及年劃分的人口、人口（不包括外籍家庭傭工）<br />\n<br />\n0-17歲：10105710人（14.48%）<br />\n18歲或以上：<span style=\"color: red;\">5999080人</span>（<span style=\"color: green;\">85.52%</span>）<br />\n總人口：7014790人<br />\n<br />\n2016年得6百萬人？<br />\n好啦，我地都要睇埋人口增長既<br />\n政府統計處網頁數據顯示2019年年底香港人口（臨時數字）有750.07萬<br />\n記住呢個數仲要包括非永久性居民<br />\n咁我地大概估算2019年底有幾多18歲或以上既香港人：<br />\n750.07萬 x <span style=\"color: green;\">85.52%</span> = 6414632人<br />\n<br />\n計埋非永久性居民既成年人都只係得大概641萬人<br />\n仲要減番非永久性居民<br />\n劏房波話700萬人既？<br />\n中間果至少59萬人（59億）去左邊？<br />\n佢係想3月31日前將59萬支那人擢升做永久性居民，定係佢打算遲幾日等政府又比人屌果陣，做戲咁話修訂至0-17歲都有一萬收？？<br />\n<br />\n望連登神探解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5cd670b9bca153b317f65092cce6c1df34a120","tid":1898668,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">響大家研究錢唔錢的時候<br />\n特衰政府已經清算手足</span><br />\nHA 清算罷工醫護<br />\n外媒記者報道<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1232553489743532032?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1232553489743532032%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X%2F4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=f94bedb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faaronmcn%2Fstatus%2F1232553489743532032%3Fs%3D21&h=f38fff00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/aaronmcn/status/1232553489743532032?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ezracheungtoto/status/1232556910894649345?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fezracheungtoto%2Fstatus%2F1232556910894649345%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X%2F4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=6fa4d32e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fezracheungtoto%2Fstatus%2F1232556910894649345%3Fs%3D21&h=caebb208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ezracheungtoto/status/1232556910894649345?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n香港記者報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sumlokkei/status/1232554841500569600?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsumlokkei%2Fstatus%2F1232554841500569600%3Fs%3D21&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X%2F4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=f24adee5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsumlokkei%2Fstatus%2F1232554841500569600%3Fs%3D21&h=d0ba2080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sumlokkei/status/1232554841